1
00:00:08,019 --> 00:00:11,400
새벽 네 시 모니터 하나 켜놓고
At four AM, with one monitor on,

2
00:00:11,948 --> 00:00:14,691
줄줄이 코드를 써 내려가
Writing line after line of code.

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:18,481
에러 백 개쯤 지우고 나면
After fixing about a hundred errors,

4
00:00:18,961 --> 00:00:21,922
캐릭터 하나가 눈을 떠
a character opens its eyes.

5
00:00:22,632 --> 00:00:29,480
아무도 모르는 이 작은 세계
This little world no one knows

6
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:33,100
내 손끝에서 태어나는 중
Is being born from my fingertips.

7
00:00:33,268 --> 00:00:37,979
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
I create dreams in the pixels,

8
00:00:37,979 --> 00:00:41,475
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, block by block.

9
00:00:42,271 --> 00:00:44,820
버그투성이 밤을 건너서
Crossing through this bug-filled night,

10
00:00:44,820 --> 00:01:07,159
나만의 게임이 시작돼
My own game begins.

11
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,959
스프라이트 하나 그려 넣으면
If I draw just one sprite,

12
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:12,438
작은 세상이 움직이잖아
This little world starts to move.

13
00:01:13,197 --> 00:01:16,203
혼자서 다 해야 하는 밤이
These nights when I do it all alone

14
00:01:16,641 --> 00:01:19,299
오히려 나를 웃게 만들어
Actually make me smile.

15
00:01:20,174 --> 00:01:24,462
완성 버튼을 누르는 그날
On the day I press the 'complete' button,

16
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:31,140
온 세상이 플레이하게 될 거야
The whole world will play it.

17
00:01:31,140 --> 00:01:36,280
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
I create dreams in the pixels,

18
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:39,730
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, block by block.

19
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:43,099
버그투성이 밤을 건너서
Crossing through this bug-filled night,

20
00:01:43,099 --> 00:01:46,700
나만의 게임이 시작돼
My own game begins.

21
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:50,299
픽셀 속의 꿈을 만들어가
I create dreams in the pixels,

22
00:01:50,299 --> 00:01:51,918
한 칸 한 칸 점프해 올라가
Jumping up, block by block.

23
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:20,896
언젠가 누군가 플레이할 때
Someday, when someone plays it,

24
00:02:21,055 --> 00:02:25,759
이 밤의 코드가 빛이 돼
The code from this night will turn into light.

